msgctxt "sn19.3:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamavagga "
msgstr "1. The First Chapter "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 3. Piṇḍasutta → maṃsapiṇḍasuttaṃ (bj) | piṇḍasakuṇiyaṃ (pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn19.3:0.3"
msgid "3. Piṇḍasutta "
msgstr "3. A Piece of Flesh "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn19.3:1.1"
msgid "“Idhāhaṃ, āvuso, gijjhakūṭā pabbatā orohanto addasaṃ maṃsapiṇḍaṃ vehāsaṃ gacchantaṃ. "
msgstr "“Just now, reverend, as I was descending from Vulture’s Peak Mountain I saw a piece of flesh flying through the air. "

msgctxt "sn19.3:1.2"
msgid "Tamenaṃ gijjhāpi kākāpi kulalāpi anupatitvā anupatitvā vitacchenti virājenti. "
msgstr "Vultures, crows, and hawks kept chasing it, pecking and clawing "

msgctxt "sn19.3:1.3"
msgid "Sā sudaṃ aṭṭassaraṃ karoti … pe … "
msgstr "as it screeched in pain. …” … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn19.3:1.4"
msgid "eso, bhikkhave, satto imasmiṃyeva rājagahe sākuṇiko ahosi … pe …. "
msgstr "“That being used to be a bird hunter right here in Rājagaha. …” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn19.3:1.5"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

